      "title": "Govt. to Gazette 22nd Amendment",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Government has decided to gazette the 22nd Amendment to the Constitution.",
        "Minister of Justice (Dr) Wijeyadasa Rajapakshe that the Cabinet approved the resolution presented by him to gazette the 22nd Amendment to the Constitution and to present it to Parliament."
